# Blade & Component Rules

## Blade Best Practices
- Use Blade templating for server-rendered views. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
- Avoid heavy logic in views; push logic to controllers/services.

## Blade Components
- Use components for reusable UI pieces.
- Prefer class-based components for complex logic.
- Use slots for flexible content injection.

